      "section": [
        "Chi blocker training camp"
      ],
      "text": "The chi blocker training camp was a secret Equalist facility used for instructing nonbenders in the art of chi blocking that was hidden in a cellar underneath a bookstore in the Dragon Flats borough. Following its discovery, it was invaded by Councilman Tarrlok, Korra, and the remainder of Tarrlok's task force. Several people who had been participating in Equalist activities at the time were captured by the task force and arrested."
    },
    {
      "body": "In 170 ${link_0}, after ${link_1}, Tarrlok created a task force to fight back against the Equalists. After recruiting ${link_2} Korra to his task force, Tarrlok planned a raid against this facility as his team's first attack.",
