      "section": [
        "Chi blocker training camp",
        "History"
      ],
      "text": "In 170 AG, after The Revelation, Tarrlok created a task force to fight back against the Equalists. After recruiting Avatar Korra to his task force, Tarrlok planned a raid against this facility as his team's first attack."
    },
    {
      "body": "The task force pumped water through the walls and froze the nearest ${link_0} blocker trainees in sight. One chi blocker threw two ${link_1} at Korra, but she quickly reacted by ${link_2} them. Two Equalists attempted to flee the camp through a system of tunnels, but were pursued and eventually captured by Avatar Korra and Tarrlok. All Equalists that had been captured on the scene were arrested shortly afterward in the presence of ${link_3}.",
